00:15:37.850 --> 00:15:42.400
The reason that the discussion
around values is so important

00:15:42.400 --> 00:15:44.940
is that values
become the structures

00:15:44.940 --> 00:15:48.050
we offer our children
within which they

00:15:48.050 --> 00:15:49.645
learn to express themselves.

00:15:52.450 --> 00:15:55.750
If we do not have clarity
around our own values,

00:15:55.750 --> 00:16:00.080
we cannot offer effective
structures to our children.

