00:53:31.030 --> 00:53:32.995
about any form of behavior.

00:53:36.360 --> 00:53:42.390
I would say that this is a very
difficult time to be alive.

00:53:42.390 --> 00:53:46.830
I would say that our
children at a very young age

00:53:46.830 --> 00:53:51.170
are dealing with the specter
of environmental destruction.

00:53:51.170 --> 00:53:54.280
There's a great sorrow in that.

00:53:54.280 --> 00:53:59.300
