00:55:02.030 --> 00:55:04.720
I would have loved
the opportunity

00:55:04.720 --> 00:55:07.300
to sit down, because there
is this phenomenon that

00:55:07.300 --> 00:55:08.030
is occurring.

00:55:08.030 --> 00:55:09.780
And this is something
that Jinpa spoke to.

00:55:09.780 --> 00:55:12.290
And it's something that I
speak to all the time, which

00:55:12.290 --> 00:55:19.310
is this split within the self
that arises in the West, which

00:55:19.310 --> 00:55:22.750
is a form of self-loathing.

00:55:22.750 --> 00:55:25.370
And it's a disease that
we have here in the West

00:55:25.370 --> 00:55:28.440
that doesn't seem to exist
so much in other places,

00:55:28.440 --> 00:55:30.880
although everyone
else is catching it.

00:55:30.880 --> 00:55:37.250
But this inner division of
the rejection of the self.

00:55:37.250 --> 00:55:39.460
And Jinpa tells a
story about this.

00:55:39.460 --> 00:55:43.920
Well, I actually-- before I got
to know Jinpa as well as I do,

00:55:43.920 --> 00:55:46.550
I used to tell this story,
because I heard this interview

00:55:46.550 --> 00:55:51.140
that he gave on "Fresh
Air" in the '90s, when

00:55:51.140 --> 00:55:55.810
Terry Gross asked him what is
the most difficult thing you've

00:55:55.810 --> 00:55:58.740
ever had to translate
for His Holiness?

00:55:58.740 --> 00:56:01.350
And he said that he was in
an East/West conference.

00:56:01.350 --> 00:56:07.520
And he translated the word
self-loathing into Tibetan.

00:56:07.520 --> 00:56:10.720
And His Holiness stopped
him and said, no, no, no no.

00:56:10.720 --> 00:56:13.890
You must be doing that wrong.

00:56:13.890 --> 00:56:15.950
That's the wrong translation.

00:56:15.950 --> 00:56:17.390
And Jinpa said, no.

00:56:17.390 --> 00:56:18.990
That's the translation.

00:56:18.990 --> 00:56:20.300
It's self-loathing.

00:56:20.300 --> 00:56:24.980
And His Holiness said, but the
self cannot loathe the self.

00:56:24.980 --> 00:56:28.970
So I mean, one of the most
erudite people on the planet

00:56:28.970 --> 00:56:32.620
did not understand that we
do have this disease here

00:56:32.620 --> 00:56:35.620
in the West, the self-loathing,
the self-- and this

00:56:35.620 --> 00:56:39.880
is one of the primary
things that I work with.

00:56:39.880 --> 00:56:43.050
I have a new book coming out
called "Coming to Peace."

00:56:43.050 --> 00:56:48.310
And it's about the
reflection of inner violence

00:56:48.310 --> 00:56:50.560
in outer relationships,
and the way

00:56:50.560 --> 00:56:55.000
that our outer relationship
express or give us information

00:56:55.000 --> 00:56:56.660
about our own inner violence.

00:56:56.660 --> 00:56:58.630
Other inner experience as well.

00:56:58.630 --> 00:57:02.230
But it's a book about
conflict resolution,

00:57:02.230 --> 00:57:06.730
basically saying that we
cannot have peace in external

00:57:06.730 --> 00:57:09.290
relationships until we
have peace in the internal

00:57:09.290 --> 00:57:11.300
relationship with ourself.

00:57:11.300 --> 00:57:16.980
And I think that there is this
idea, this scientific idea--

00:57:16.980 --> 00:57:18.760
what is this self?

00:57:18.760 --> 00:57:20.170
This is not scientific.

00:57:20.170 --> 00:57:21.190
We can't prove it.

00:57:21.190 --> 00:57:22.340
You know, what is this?

00:57:22.340 --> 00:57:26.870
And there's rejection of spirit,
this rejection of the soul,

00:57:26.870 --> 00:57:29.120
this rejection of the
deeper part of the self,

00:57:29.120 --> 00:57:33.560
which is extremely
unscientific to just reject

00:57:33.560 --> 00:57:34.970
this aspect of experience.

00:57:34.970 --> 00:57:38.170
And so people don't
have tools, they

00:57:38.170 --> 00:57:41.840
don't have vocabulary
to speak to this kind

00:57:41.840 --> 00:57:45.320
of inner dislocation
that they experience,

00:57:45.320 --> 00:57:51.280
because there's nothing
rational or replicable about it.

00:57:51.280 --> 00:57:57.090
And yet, people suffer deeply
internally because they cannot

00:57:57.090 --> 00:57:58.800
rest in themselves.

00:57:58.800 --> 00:58:01.200
And one of the reasons they
cannot rest in themselves is

00:58:01.200 --> 00:58:03.160
because they look around them.

00:58:03.160 --> 00:58:04.380
There's so much violence.

00:58:04.380 --> 00:58:06.600
There's no place
to rest externally.

00:58:06.600 --> 00:58:08.300
They go inside themselves.

00:58:08.300 --> 00:58:10.250
They haven't been able
to develop resources

00:58:10.250 --> 00:58:12.340
because everyone says there's
no such thing as spirit,

00:58:12.340 --> 00:58:14.506
there's no such thing as
soul, there's no such thing

00:58:14.506 --> 00:58:15.335
as the deeper self.

00:58:15.335 --> 00:58:17.640
And so they're left
with this emptiness.

00:58:17.640 --> 00:58:18.480
Right?

00:58:18.480 --> 00:58:21.420
